<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;" class="">
              You can search for the bus and start booking with Hoang Long with these simple steps:
          </font></font></p>
          <p></p><h3><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">1. Search for a ride</font></font></h3><p></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the "Online booking" section you choose the destination, destination, travel dates in accordance with the requirements. </font></font></p>
          <p>
              </p><h3><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">2. Select a bus trip</font></font></h3>
          <p></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">
              Trips that match your requirements will be displayed in the search results section. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The result will display itinerary time, estimated departure time, estimated arrival time, fares (including meals). </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Please click "Select flight" to continue.
          </font></font></p>
          <p>
              </p><h3><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">3. Passenger</font></font></h3>
          <p></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the "Customer information" section, please fill in the required information including: full name, phone number, email, address.</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the "Transaction form" section, please select the transaction method &amp; payment. </font><font class="" style="vertical-align: inherit;">Hoang Long offers 04 payment methods including:</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">(1) Direct payment upon ticket receipt</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">(2) ATM transfer payment</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">(3) Pay for local ATM cards online</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">(4) International card payment: visa, master</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the "Transport conditions" section, please read carefully before using Hoang Long's passenger transportation service and continue to book tickets.</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">After completing the above information, please confirm by clicking "I agree with the terms of service" and click </font></font><strong><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">"Confirm booking"</font></font></strong></p>
          <p>
              </p><h3><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">4. Confirm the booking information</font></font></h3>
          <p></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">The system will display "Confirmation of booking information", you enter the security code and confirmation of booking. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Hoang Long system will automatically transfer ticket code, booking information and customer information to your registered email.</font></font></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">In case you choose the payment method is (03) and (04) the system will perform additional steps of online payment through the online payment gateway OnePay.</font></font></p>
          <p>
              </p><h3><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">5. Payment &amp; seat completion</font></font></h3>
          <p></p>
          <p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">After successful payment via online payment gateway Onepay ( </font></font><a href="http://202.9.84.88/documents/payment/1vn.html" target="_blank"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Payment guide</font></font></a><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"> ). </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">You will be transferred to Hoang Long system with the step of selecting the number of seats and the boarding point in the province of departure. </font><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Finish the buying process with the "Complete" button.</font></font></p>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>